# Feature 13: Frontend Layout with Responsive Sidebar Navigation

## Summary
Implemented a responsive frontend layout with sidebar navigation, header, and main content area for the PMP 2026 Study Application.

## Components Created

### 1. Sidebar Component (`src/components/layout/Sidebar.tsx`)
- Responsive sidebar that collapses on mobile
- Mobile backdrop overlay with click-to-close
- Navigation links: Dashboard, Flashcards, Practice Tests, Progress
- ECO Domains section with People (33%), Process (41%), Business Environment (26%)
- PMP 2026 ECO footer info
- Active state highlighting based on current route
- Smooth slide-in animation for mobile

### 2. Header Component (`src/components/layout/Header.tsx`)
- Mobile hamburger menu button
- Page title and description area
- Search bar (desktop) / search button (mobile)
- Notifications button with badge
- Settings button
- User avatar dropdown button
- Sticky positioning at top

### 3. MainLayout Component (`src/components/layout/MainLayout.tsx`)
- Combines Sidebar and Header with main content area
- Manages sidebar open/close state for mobile
- Full-height layout with overflow handling
- Responsive padding for content area

### 4. Index Export (`src/components/layout/index.ts`)
- Clean barrel export for all layout components

## Styling Updates

### globals.css
- Updated CSS variables for light/dark mode
- Custom scrollbar styling
- Focus styles for accessibility
- Utility classes: text-gradient, card-hover, scrollbar-hide
- Component classes: btn-primary, btn-secondary, card, input, badge variants, progress-bar

### tailwind.config.ts
- Added PMP domain colors (people/blue, process/green, business/purple)
- Custom font families using Geist fonts
- Custom animations: fade-in, slide-in, scale-in
- Dark mode support via media query

## Root Layout Update
- Integrated MainLayout wrapper
- Updated metadata for PMP 2026 Study App

